76561197997718411,Recommended,238750,15318650,"Posted: 12 April, 2015",all,freeform1111,"A good old school rpg not without its flaws. First of all, the story and the lore is nothing to write home about in my opinion. Furthermore, I like the grid-based style dungeon crawler but it is really quite strange to use the grid-based movement in an open enviroment. Besides, it is really quite annoyed that you can't move when one enemy is adjacent of you and some other enemies are shooting at you from the distance. There is also some technical problem involving some low FPS that I encounter during somewhere on the world map. Other annoyed little problems including no space to store your items & equipment, obscure puzzle and that you can't scroll the map.Although the game has some problem, it still has some good old-school fun including challenging combat, nice dungeons full of traps, monsters, treasures and puzzles and finally  the planning and  buidling of your party. If you can stand its rough edges and you enjoy old school rpg, you may find it worthwhile to try this game."
,Not Recommended,238750,15327798,"Posted: 12 April, 2015",all,ppkk,"It seems that this game is an attempt to recreate spirit of Might & Magic 3 (year 1991). Sounds quite nice to people (including me) who like M&M 3 or Xeen themed ones (3-5 and Swords of Xeen).Graphics are quite good, but not spectacular.The biggest problem for me is that they recreated M&M 3 played on lower end (for 1991) computer. It is not too responsive, actions take too much time. And there was not much difference between highest and lowest graphics settings, so this lethargy was game design decision, not insufficient power of my computer. And to make things worse, there are fewer fast travelling options (no Time Distortion, Teleport or Jump spells; and ""Lloyd's Beacon"" [Spirit Beacon] is not early accessible).There is no arena too, by the way. And no working bank. And no science-fiction elements.So, the game does not look good for either M&M 3-5 or M&M 6-9 fans. Those who did not like M&M 3-9 would not like this one too, those who did not play M&M 3-9 would better play them before this game."
